name: Dr. Click
description: In my almost 10 years of photography, this is for sure my favorite picture, not because of the complexity of the photographic work. At that moment I was someone with a lot of dreams and no clue how I could make them happen. This picture is about a doctor supporting one of his sons for the thousandth time. My father to me has been a doctor, a carpenter, painter, friend, enemy, savior, partner, and among many other things photographer.  Love you dad. This picture was taken 3/2/2012, dad was 52.
